        <h2>What's New in 0.5.72</h2>
        <h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed crashes that could occur when closing the plugin in Ableton Live</li>
          <li>Fixed diagnostic report uploads failing for Ableton crash log files</li>
          <li>Fixed broken download links in diagnostic reports for files with spaces in their names</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="source">Build 1132 &middot; <a href="https://github.com/danielraffel/PlunderTube/commit/c53d2c41">c53d2c41</a> on main</p>
